        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> (manipulate)</p><hr /><p>A <em>restful salve</em> is a compound that can be applied to the skin to prevent undeath. If applied to a fresh corpse, the corpse doesn't decay, nor can it be transformed into an undead or otherwise controlled until the sun rises the next morning. If applied to a living creature, this salve lasts for only 1 hour due to the body's natural excretions. For that duration, the salve wards off effects that would cause undeath upon dying.</p>"
